---
title: Bacon Penne Arrabiata topped with Parmesan & Parsley
description: Arrabiata may mean “angry” in Italian, but we feel anything but mad about this deliciously spicy dish. Our chefs cooked up this twist on the classic Italian meal, adding savory and crispy bacon to the mix. We’re pretty sure the fiery, tomato-ey, carby goodness will transport you to that favorite Italian restaurant only you and your BFFs know about.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bacon-penne-arrabiata-acc037dc.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/bacon-penne-arrabiata-60510cb2b1b45d1d1a21532b-34082927.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/bacon-penne-arrabiata-60510cb2b1b45d1d1a21532b
